New Records: Iceland achieved their highest score in the UEFA Nations League with a 2-0 win over Montenegro
Key Match Events: O. Óskarsson scored the first goal for Iceland in the 39th minute
J. Þorsteinsson scored the second goal for Iceland in the 58th minute
J. Guðmunds­son and G. Sigurðsson provided assists for Iceland's goals
Miscellaneous Highlights: The match was played at Laugardalsvöllur in front of 4,683 spectators
